bitfields.name: XSPI_DELAY_CELL_NUM
bitfields.description:
Fuse configured SLV_DLY_COARSE in DLLCR. The value in the field is multiplied by kxSpiHighdllDelayCellUnit_Min to calculate the read delay in each delay tap.  
The read delay for each delay tap is calculated as : 
XSPI_DELAY_CELL_NUM * kxSpiHighdllDelayCellUnit_Min(ps)
where kxSpiHighdllDelayCellUnit_Min = 30ps
Note: This fuse only works when frequency is under 60M for external input DQS.
